window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>\"An aerialist, a performer, an eclectic rising starâ€”please welcome the Maximalist!\"</b></p> <p>Max has finally made it to the stage. As he shoots for the stars, the last thing he expects is to fall into the arms of the most striking aliens he's ever seen.</p> <p>Moss has never been so charmed by a human before. A simple touch pulls them both into a passionate heat that can only be relieved in bed. But below all the lust and desire, there is a simmering bond that will bring them closer in more ways than one.</p> <p>When trouble arises, Max and Moss have no choice but to take center stage. Can their cosmic connection conquer all?</p> <p><i>This alien romance has a nonbinary Intersex alien, tentacles, toys, and other things, fated mates love, a super fast burn, swoony romance, and delicious spice.</i></p> <p>Cosmic Heat <i>is book three in the Galactic Gems series. Each book will follow a different performer finding their alien love, spicy scenes, and lots of romance with a dash of mystery. They can be enjoyed as standalones, although there will be character cross-over.</i></p>"; 
